          "message": "docs(recipes): add DeepSeek-V4 usage guide (#713)\n\nAdds recipes/DeepSeek-V4.md covering DeepSeek-V4-Pro on 8xMI355X TP=8\nFP8 KV cache. Includes the required ATOM_USE_TRITON_MOE=1 launch env\n(missing it silently degrades GSM8K from ~0.95 to ~0.6 via fallback\npath), a 1024/1024 throughput sweep at concurrency 4..256 measured\n2026-05-07 on commit 33c54649, and the GSM8K nshot=5 baseline\n(flexible-extract 0.9530, strict-match 0.9538). Recipe links to the\nbenchmark dashboard for the latest cross-commit numbers.",
