          "message": "Remove chunk split in Qwen3.5 and Qwen3Next (#682)\n\n* remove chunk split\n\nSigned-off-by: ganyi <ygan@amd.com>\n\n* fix accuracy\n\nSigned-off-by: ganyi <ygan@amd.com>\n\n* add None input for not quantize case\n\nSigned-off-by: ganyi <ygan@amd.com>\n\n* fix ci\n\nSigned-off-by: ganyi <ygan@amd.com>\n\n* maybe fix the ci benchmark crash\n\nSigned-off-by: ganyi <ygan@amd.com>\n\n* add env var for bare atom acc test\n\nSigned-off-by: ganyi <ygan@amd.com>\n\n* add fp8 kv cache for qwen3next bare atom ci\n\nSigned-off-by: ganyi <ygan@amd.com>\n\n* make fusion as default\n\nSigned-off-by: ganyi <ygan@amd.com>\n\n* disable non-persistent pa\n\nSigned-off-by: ganyi <ygan@amd.com>\n\n* add num tokens\n\nSigned-off-by: ganyi <ygan@amd.com>\n\n---------\n\nSigned-off-by: ganyi <ygan@amd.com>",
